    "Although ChatGPT's ability to answer parasitology questions was not comparable to that of the medical students of Korea, the responses provided by ChatGPT had an acceptable explanation for the questions [19].",
    "In contrast, in this study, we found that ChatGPT surpassed the mean score of the students.",
    "This might be due to the varied methodology applied compared to that adopted in previous studies.",
    "The Korean study was specific to the field of parasitology, and the medical students were administered the exam immediately after completing the module.",
    "In contrast, in this study, students were answering questions related to the entire syllabus of community medicine that they had been learning for 3 years."
  ],
